9. Qc2 Bg4
{ Getting the bishop out immediately is the most active way.  9...O-O  is also fine. }
10. Ne5 { 10.Bd3  Nbd7= } 10... Be6
{ White has gotten Ne5 'for free' but in fact it's going to hurt him as the knight will have to retreat to avoid the c5-push. }
11. f4 { This is too optimistic. } 11... c5
{ Again, if White ever takes on c5, then e3 will be as weak as d5. } *

