{ Black is perhaps not exactly worse here, but it does look a bit more pleasant for White. Still, it's a matter of taste and I have played these positions myself a fair bit with OK results. }
15... Qe7 16. Rae1 Bd7
{ Trying to create some slight disharmony before going ...c5. } 17. Nc1 c5
