7. Nc3 O-O 8. Rc1
{ Played against me by the Danish #2, Grandmaster Mads Andersen. } 8... dxc4
{ This works well here, as Rc1 is not the most influential developing move. }
9. Bxc4 b5 10. Be2 Bb7 11. O-O c5
{ Given one more move Black is completely equal. } 12. dxc5 { The only test. }
12... Nxc5 13. Nxb5 { But it all works out fairly well for us. } 13... axb5 14.
