9... b5 { An absolutely essential move. } 10. Qb3
{ 10.Qd3  Bb7  is very similar. } 10... Bb7 11. Rd1
{ Threatening a discovered attack, so we need to get our queen out of the way. }
11... Bxg2 12. Kxg2 Qb7+ 13. Qf3
{ White's best move, but it is not enough to pose real problems in the ending. }
13... Qxf3+ 14. Nxf3 Be7 15. Nbd2 { The critical move! } 15... O-O 16. Nb3 Rc8
{ Followed by ...Nc6 or ...Nbd7 is just equal. } *

