{ The solid approach. We try to trade material in the centre. } 6. O-O cxd4 7.
Nxd4 Nf6
{ 7...e5?  8.Nf3  Qxd1  9.Rxd1  Compared to7. Qxd4, White got an extra move, Rd1, which we can't allow!  9...Nc6  10.Nbd2!  f6  11.Nxc4  Be6  12.b3  and Rd1 is a huge tempo to have gained here, as Nd6+ will soon be on the agenda! }
