{ White's best move, but it is not enough to pose real problems in the ending. }
13... Qxf3+ 14. Nxf3 Be7 15. a4 bxa4
{ Very important! Without the queens on the b-file this is possible, and by trading the otherwise weak b-pawn we we get rid of the main weakness. }
16. Rxa4 O-O
