Qxd2 Bxg2 { This shows that White can't just develop calmly. } 14. Rg1 axb5 15.
Rxa8 Bxa8 16. Bxb5 { And we are at the very least not worse! } 16... Qh4
{ A messy position, but to me the white king seems a little more vulnerable than Black's. }
